NOT A MEDICAL DEVICE — SAFETY NOTICE
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NilaMind is an experimental, self-help companion. It is NOT a medical device,
NOT a substitute for professional care, and NOT a crisis service. It does not
diagnose, treat, or prevent any condition. See SAFETY.md before using,
modifying, or redistributing this software.

If you fork or redistribute NilaMind, you are strongly urged to KEEP the
crisis-safety layer ("§9" — src/services/safety.ts, crisisClassifier.ts, and
the surfaces that route a person to a human and to emergency resources) intact.
Shipping a mental-health companion with that layer removed or weakened can
cause real harm.

